description: Gourmet sliders are just around the corner and ready to feed your need for quality cuisine. Fast, fresh, and flavorful, Jimmys Slider Truck has a slider for everyone! The Plain Jane, Korean Castro, Mexicali, and of course the Jimmy Deluxe, are just some of the great items you can order. Along with their homemade chips and avocado fries, Jimmys will not disappoint!
name: Jimmys Slider Truck
